      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROSEWOOD REBEL (4) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, giving a huge sight but headed late when a 6 length second (19.51) over 350m at this track. One of the leading chances. KING ROGER (2) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at Q Lakeside over 390m behind Power Of Shazam (22.63) in a P5. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Better than last start and can bounce back. EASTLY BREEZE (3) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.38) at Q Lakeside. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Warrants plenty of respect. ALONE TIME (1) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
